{"data":[{"id":561504321,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a6d097ecf988531814d448865697be3d","url_token":"luo-hua-sheng-23-46","name":"罗化生","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ebb1c461788a19a1cb71e7e4c1bd7664_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ebb1c461788a19a1cb71e7e4c1bd7664_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a6d097ecf988531814d448865697be3d","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":1457,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561504321","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545973437,"updated_time":1545974116,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e题主还是一个高中生，视野确实容易比较狭隘，说一下个人的经历以及个人证明哥德巴赫猜想的历程。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当年还在读高中的时候，也觉得考上清华北大是无上的荣光，是追求的一个重大的目标。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但几年以后，随着心态的平和，对于考上什么大学，获得什么学位之类的根本不放在心上了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只要你有自己的研究成果，干嘛一定要有什么学位？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e即使暂时没有学术成果，自己自由自在的探索也够了，毕竟数学这个东西有一个好处就是不需要实验室，反过来说如果在某些研究院所里，各种禁锢的可能更多。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这里很多人对题主进行嘲讽，是中国教育缺乏最重要的一环：尊重教育的体现，不必在意。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e个人研究过哥德巴赫猜想，我估计你的证明很可能存在一些逻辑上的不严谨。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是不管怎么样，敢于探索，敢于思考总是好事，你可能证明哥德巴赫猜想不成功，但是你最少锤炼了你的思维，这是有助于你以后的探索其他领域的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然了，也不要过分的陷进去，毕竟你追求的是数学，而不是证明成功后的荣誉，除了哥德巴赫猜想，还有非常广阔的天地。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以下是我对哥德巴赫猜想证明的一些结果\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e满足\u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/search?q=%E5%93%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%B7%B4%E8%B5%AB%E7%8C%9C%E6%83%B3\u0026amp;source=Entity\u0026amp;hybrid_search_source=Entity\u0026amp;hybrid_search_extra=%7B%22sourceType%22%3A%22answer%22%2C%22sourceId%22%3A561454475%7D\" class=\"internal\"\u003e哥德巴赫猜想\u003c/a\u003e的素数对的配对数 大致为\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=Gd_%7Bx%7D%3D%5Cprod_%7Bp_%7Bl%7D%2Fx%7Dx%281-1%2Fp_%7Bl%7D%29%281-2%2Fp%29%2B%5Csum_%7Bp%3D3%7D%5E%7B%5Csqrt%7Bx%7D%7D%5Csum_%7Bl%3D1%7D%5E%7Bq-1%7D%27%5Csum_%7Bt%3D1%7D%5E%7Bf%7D%5Cmu_%7Bq%7D%5Cmu_%7Bt%7D%7Bh%2Fq%28%28%5Cpi_%7Bt%7D%28x%2Cq%2Cl%29-%5Cpi_%7Bt%7D%28x%29%2F%5Cvarphi%28q%29%29%7D\" alt=\"Gd_{x}=\\prod_{p_{l}/x}x(1-1/p_{l})(1-2/p)+\\sum_{p=3}^{\\sqrt{x}}\\sum_{l=1}^{q-1}'\\sum_{t=1}^{f}\\mu_{q}\\mu_{t}{h/q((\\pi_{t}(x,q,l)-\\pi_{t}(x)/\\varphi(q))}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e上式中\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eq为素数p以及素数p的乘积\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ep不整除于x\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=hx%5Cequiv+l%28modq%29\" alt=\"hx\\equiv l(modq)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Csum%E2%80%98\" alt=\"\\sum‘\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 表示对q的缩系求和\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cpi_%7Bt%7D\" alt=\"\\pi_{t}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e (x)表示小于x的t个素数的积\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ef为小于x 的n个素数乘积的最大的n值\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可以看到后面那一项是比较复杂的，而这一项我本来以为很简单，但是就有一个逻辑漏洞感觉处理不掉，然后苦苦思索了一年多，才发现一个看似初等的问题，实际上就是一个解析数论即等差数列中的素数定理的问题，而要解决这个问题，证明第二项是一个相对小的数，我还需要继续探索。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说明一下曾经让我困惑的那个看起来很初等的问题是\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对于一个整数X和两个素数p,q\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如何判定X=np+mq这个式子成立\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e并不是X越大，就一定成立\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e例如12=5+7\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是比12大的13就没有相应的式子成立，思索这个问题，我思索了一年，才发现必须转换为解析数论问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e总之，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1要估计问题的困难性\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2，敢于探索值得肯定\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3，不要只关注这个问题，如果对数学感兴趣，你完全可以接着自学大学数学课程，发现广阔天地，然后找到真正属于你的领域。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"题主还是一个高中生，视野确实容易比较狭隘，说一下个人的经历以及个人证明哥德巴赫猜想的历程。当年还在读高中的时候，也觉得考上清华北大是无上的荣光，是追求的一个重大的目标。但几年以后，随着心态的平和，对于考上什么大学，获得什么学位之类的根本不…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=359\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=357\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","totals":1885}}
